      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.219-12</ph> Special 8(a) Subcontract Conditions.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     href="19.811-3.dita#FAR_19_811_3"
                     base="i1100084"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.811-3</xref>(b)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3284e15">Special 8(a) Subcontract Conditions <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Oct 2019)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol id="d3248e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The Small Business Administration (SBA) has entered into Contract No.<cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e33"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="GFI">________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert number of contract</i>]</cite> with the <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e39"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="GFI">_________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert name of contracting agency</i>]</cite> to furnish the supplies or services as described therein. A copy of the contract is attached hereto and made a part hereof.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e38">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e54"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="GFI">___________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert name of subcontractor</i>],</cite> hereafter referred to as the subcontractor, agrees and acknowledges as follows:</p>
               <ol id="d3248e53" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e50">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                That it will, for and on behalf of the SBA, fulfill and perform all of the requirements of Contract No. <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                              xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e70"
                              class="- topic/cite "
                              xtrf="GFI">______ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert number of contract</i>]</cite> for the consideration stated therein and that it has read and is familiar with each and every part of the contract.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e61">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                That the SBA has delegated responsibility, except for novation agreements, for the administration of this subcontract to the <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                              xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e85"
                              class="- topic/cite "
                              xtrf="GFI">_______ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert name of contracting agency</i>]</cite> with complete authority to take any action on behalf of the Government under the terms and conditions of this subcontract.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e72">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                That it will notify the <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                              xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e103"
                              class="- topic/cite "
                              xtrf="GFI">__________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert name of contracting agency</i>]</cite> Contracting Officer in writing immediately upon entering an agreement (either oral or written) to transfer all or part of its stock or other ownership interest to any other party.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3284e83">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            Payments, including any progress payments under this subcontract, will be made directly to the subcontractor by the <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrc="52.219-12_d3272e120"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="GFI">______ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert name of contracting agency</i>]</cite>.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
